author: The Press-Enterprise
title: Matt Damon, Bruno Mars, Chevy Chase: Oct. 8 celebrity birthdays
text:
The Associated Press
Published: Oct. 8, 2015 Updated: 12:01 p.m. Actor Paul Hogan is 76.
Actor-comedian Chevy Chase is 72.
Country singer Susan Raye is 71.
TV personality Sarah Purcell (“Real People”) is 67.
Actress Sigourney Weaver is 66.
Singer Robert “Kool” Bell of Kool and the Gang is 65.
Comedian Darrell Hammond is 60.
Singer Steve Perry of Cherry Poppin’ Daddies is 52.
Actor Ian Hart (“Dirt”) is 51.
Singer CeCe Winans is 51.
Bassist C.J. Ramone of the Ramones is 50.
Actress Karyn Parsons (“The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air”) is 49.
Singer Teddy Riley is 49.
Actress Emily Procter (“CSI: Miami”) is 47.
Actor-screenwriter Matt Damon is 45.
Singer Byron Reeder of Mista is 36.
Actor Nick Cannon is 35.
Singer-songwriter Bruno Mars is 30.
Actor Angus T. Jones (“Two and a Half Men”) is 22.
Birthdays of the past:
1895 Juan Perón , Argentine dictator; died 1974.
